           SHORT='Itex2mml transforms webpages with embedded itex into XHTML and MathML'
cat << EOF
Itex2mml transforms webpages with embedded itex (a dialect of latex) into xhtml
and MathML pages, suitable for viewing with Mozilla.

If you are comfortable with latex, and wish to create documents primarily for
viewing on the web, then itex2mml may be for you.
EOF
